```text
BEGIN

Create a 3x3 game board with all spaces empty

Set current player to X
Set game status to running

WHILE game is running

    Display the game board

    Ask current player to enter a row number
    Ask current player to enter a column number

    IF selected position is outside the board
        Display "Invalid move"
        Continue to next loop iteration
    END IF

    IF selected position is already occupied
        Display "Square already taken"
        Continue to next loop iteration
    END IF

    Place current player symbol in selected position

    Check all rows for matching symbols
    Check all columns for matching symbols
    Check both diagonals for matching symbols

    IF current player has three matching symbols
        Display game board
        Display current player wins
        End game
    END IF

    IF all board positions are filled
        Display game board
        Display draw game
        End game
    END IF

    IF current player is X
        Change current player to O
    ELSE
        Change current player to X
    END IF

END WHILE

END
```
